mathematica: nmax = 60; CoefficientList[Series[Product[((1 - x^(2*k-1)) * (1 - x^(6*k-3)))^3, {k, 1, nmax}], {x, 0, nmax}], x] (* _Vaclav Kotesovec_, Nov 07 2015 *)
eta[q_]:= q^(1/24)*QPochhammer[q]; a:= CoefficientList[Series[q^(1/2)*(eta[q]*eta[q^3]/(eta[q^2]*eta[q^6]))^3, {q, 0, 60}], q]; Table[a[[n]], {n, 1, 50}] (* _G. C. Greubel_, Jun 03 2018 *)
